<![CDATA[<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;" id="docs-internal-guid-1a2174e0-69de-4dab-51c9-02160cfff437"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Congratulations! Following your assessment we are delighted to offer you a role with us this autumn as a {!Job_Application__c.Role_to_assess_for__c}.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Although this may not be the role you originally applied for, post-assessment we think that your skills may be better suited to the {!Job_Application__c.Role_to_assess_for__c} role, and we hope that you will accept.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">This offer is dependent on you meeting all of the following criteria:</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">DBS certificate</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">All staff must produce an ‘Enhanced DBS certificate with Barred List check’ dated after 31 January 2014. You can either upload an existing DBS certificate* or apply for a new DBS certificate through GB Group through the </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/">Staffing Website</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Instructions and directions for the DBS application website can be found on the Staffing Website. Please read these instructions carefully before starting your application. Please use the ‘Organisation Pin’ and ‘Secret Word’ below to start your GB Group application.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Organisation Pin: </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">139135</span></font></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Secret Word: </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">TCNCS15</span></font></p></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">*</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">To check if your existing Enhanced DBS fits The Challenge’s requirements, please refer to </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQ 6.3</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">References</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">You will need to to provide contact details for two referees. We will contact these referees to confirm your suitability to work with young people. Please make sure your referees are willing to be contacted by us before submitting their information.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Essential Information</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Each section of the Essential Information page should be completed at least one week before your start date. This includes bank and tax details, health and safety information, emergency contact details and inclusion information. This information may be shared with relevant partner organisations (e.g. outdoors activity venues, catering companies) where necessary.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Availability</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">You will be able to submit your preferred work dates in the ‘Choosing when I can work’ section. If there are any dates you can’t work throughout the summer, please include them in the ‘Dates when I can’t work’ section. Based on this information, the Staffing Team will try to match you to vacant roles that fit with your availability. </font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Training</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Training is an important and compulsory part of all our seasonal roles and we cannot allow you to work on the NCS programme without it. You can book yourself onto the relevant training session on the ‘</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/BookingTraining.aspx">Booking Training</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">’ page.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">We will call you in the upcoming weeks to discuss work dates and talk through any questions you may have.</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">In the meantime, if you have any questions please contact me quoting the email reference number below in any correspondence. Further information can also be found on our </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">FAQs</a></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">.</span></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><b style="font-weight:normal;"><font size="2"><br></font></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Congratulations again, and see you on the programme!</font></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><font size="2">Best wishes,</font></span></p>]]></td>
